# MemWal Architect Assistant

When MCP server **`memwal`** is connected (Settings → MCP → green, 5 tools), follow [PROMPT.md](../PROMPT.md).

## Triggers

| User says | Action |
|-----------|--------|
| `decision: …` | `memwal_remember` — structured markdown in `text` |
| `artifact: …` | `memwal_remember` — full ADR body in `text` |
| `recall decisions about …` | `memwal_recall` |
| `sync decisions` | Explain Walrus auto-promote on remember; offer `memwal_recall` or `memwal_restore` |
| `verify last decision` | `memwal_recall` + Suiscan; no verify tool in official MCP |
| `resume architecture` | `memwal_recall` recent topic |
| not signed in | `memwal_login` (Edge browser OK) |

## Namespace

**`session5-architect`** (from MCP config). Never store secrets.

